headline: Malema Wins 2025 Best of West Award for Ultrasonic Flow Controller, Advancing Innovation in Semiconductor Manufacturing
summary: Malema™, part of PSG and Dover (NYSE: DOV) and a leading provider of flow meter technologies for use in industrial and semiconductor applications, today announced that its LFC-7650 Series Ultrasonic Flow Controller has been named the winner of the 2025 Best of West Award presented by SEMI Americas and Semiconductor Digest at SEMICON® West.
